	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey, im gonna start an SK and I need to know what race is best for SK. I dont know much about them, i dont know if Sks are better at Casting or Tanking so i would just like to know what you think i should be for an SK, thanks.<br>&nbsp;<br>matty</td></tr>
