<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%>
	   <a name=103603111455827></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f103603111455827><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=5&mid=103603111455827>RE: What Race is best for SK?!?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=5&mid=103603111455827#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=145263><span id=Scholar>lunaticfringesk</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>217 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Oct 30th 9:45 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.65]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is essentially an impossible question to answer.&nbsp;&nbsp;The definition of &quot;best&quot; is very subjective.  I will tell yoo, however, that there is no doubt that a SK is a far better tank than he is a caster.  <br><br>All I can personally tell you are my favorites.  If I was going to start my SK all over again, I would probably be a Gnome or an Ogre.  The Gnome, because he levels the fastest of all the other SK races, or the Ogre, because he has the best overall stats.<br><br>They would be the best for me, but that sure as hell doesnt mean that they are the best for everyone else.  <br><br>The most popular SK is the Dark Elf.  At the moment, I think Verant made a mistake.  If I understand correctly, Gnomes level faster than Dark Elves.  Well, since they have better overall stats, yet still level faster, Im still trying to figure out why (save for roleplay or something) anyone would want to be a DE SK now.  Gnomes seem to be the better choice.  I must be missing something, but I cant find anything yet...  /shrug<br><br>At the end of the day, pick the one you think you would have the most fun with.  As lame as that answer may be, its probably the best advice you are going to get<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
