	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Gnome does NOT level the fastest of all the Shadow Knight races. Here's how exp works for the races SKs can be:<br><br>(100 is the median, and only the Halfling gets a bonus, at 95)<br><br>100 - Human<br>100 - Dark Elf<br>100 - Gnome<br>100 - Erudite<br>115 - Ogre<br>120 - Troll<br>120 - Iksar<br><br>This number is used as a multiplier interally by the game to determine the amount of exp you need to get a level. This means that Ogres, Trolls, and Iksars level more slowly. At low levels, this is fairly painless, but it gets considerably worse after about level 50, so I've heard.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Oct 31 03:37:52 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
